<p:notes xmlns:a="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/drawingml/2006/main" xmlns:r="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/officeDocument/2006/relationships" xmlns:p="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/presentationml/2006/main"><p:cSld><p:spTree><p:nvGrpSpPr><p:cNvPr id="1" name=""/><p:cNvGrpSpPr/><p:nvPr/></p:nvGrpSpPr><p:grpSpPr><a:xfrm><a:off x="0" y="0"/><a:ext cx="0" cy="0"/><a:chOff x="0" y="0"/><a:chExt cx="0" cy="0"/></a:xfrm></p:grpSpPr><p:sp><p:nvSpPr><p:cNvPr id="2" name="幻灯片图像占位符 1"/><p:cNvSpPr><a:spLocks noGrp="1" noRot="1" noChangeAspect="1"/></p:cNvSpPr><p:nvPr><p:ph type="sldImg" idx="2"/></p:nvPr></p:nvSpPr><p:spPr/></p:sp><p:sp><p:nvSpPr><p:cNvPr id="3" name="文本占位符 2"/><p:cNvSpPr><a:spLocks noGrp="1"/></p:cNvSpPr><p:nvPr><p:ph type="body" idx="3"/></p:nvPr></p:nvSpPr><p:spPr/><p:txBody><a:bodyPr/><a:lstStyle/><a:p><a:endParaRPr><a:latin typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:ea typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:cs typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:sym typeface="+mn-ea"/></a:endParaRPr></a:p><a:p><a:r><a:rPr><a:latin typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:ea typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:cs typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:sym typeface="+mn-ea"/></a:rPr><a:t>在无监督表示学习中，编码器的对比损失是一种用于训练编码器模型的损失函数，旨在使相似样本之间的表示更加接近，而不相似样本之间的表示则更远离。</a:t></a:r><a:endParaRPr><a:latin typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:ea typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:cs typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:sym typeface="+mn-ea"/></a:endParaRPr></a:p><a:p><a:endParaRPr><a:latin typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:ea typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:cs typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:sym typeface="+mn-ea"/></a:endParaRPr></a:p><a:p><a:r><a:rPr><a:latin typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:ea typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:cs typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:sym typeface="+mn-ea"/></a:rPr><a:t>主要特点：</a:t></a:r><a:endParaRPr><a:latin typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:ea typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:cs typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:sym typeface="+mn-ea"/></a:endParaRPr></a:p><a:p><a:r><a:rPr><a:latin typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:ea typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:cs typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:sym typeface="+mn-ea"/></a:rPr><a:t>无监督学习： 不需要标记的标签，利用未标记的数据自动学习特征表示。</a:t></a:r><a:endParaRPr><a:latin typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:ea typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:cs typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:sym typeface="+mn-ea"/></a:endParaRPr></a:p><a:p><a:r><a:rPr><a:latin typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:ea typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:cs typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:sym typeface="+mn-ea"/></a:rPr><a:t>特征提取： 通过学习数据的内在结构和模式，提取有意义的特征表示，以用于后续任务。</a:t></a:r><a:endParaRPr><a:latin typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:ea typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:cs typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:sym typeface="+mn-ea"/></a:endParaRPr></a:p><a:p><a:r><a:rPr><a:latin typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:ea typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:cs typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:sym typeface="+mn-ea"/></a:rPr><a:t>无监督预训练是指在没有标签数据的情况下，利用大量未标记数据预训练模型，然后将其权重或表示迁移或微调到监督学习任务中，从而提高监督学习模型的性能。</a:t></a:r><a:endParaRPr><a:latin typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:ea typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:cs typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:sym typeface="+mn-ea"/></a:endParaRPr></a:p><a:p><a:endParaRPr><a:latin typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:ea typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:cs typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:sym typeface="+mn-ea"/></a:endParaRPr></a:p><a:p><a:r><a:rPr><a:latin typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:ea typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:cs typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:sym typeface="+mn-ea"/></a:rPr><a:t>无监督预训练的步骤：</a:t></a:r><a:endParaRPr><a:latin typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:ea typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:cs typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:sym typeface="+mn-ea"/></a:endParaRPr></a:p><a:p><a:r><a:rPr><a:latin typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:ea typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:cs typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:sym typeface="+mn-ea"/></a:rPr><a:t>预训练阶段： 利用未标记数据进行预训练，通常使用自编码器、生成模型或其他无监督方法。</a:t></a:r><a:endParaRPr><a:latin typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:ea typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:cs typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:sym typeface="+mn-ea"/></a:endParaRPr></a:p><a:p><a:r><a:rPr><a:latin typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:ea typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:cs typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:sym typeface="+mn-ea"/></a:rPr><a:t>微调阶段： 将预训练模型的权重或表示迁移到监督学习任务中，作为初始参数进行微调。</a:t></a:r><a:endParaRPr><a:latin typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:ea typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:cs typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:sym typeface="+mn-ea"/></a:endParaRPr></a:p><a:p><a:r><a:rPr><a:latin typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:ea typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:cs typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:sym typeface="+mn-ea"/></a:rPr><a:t>无监督预训练可提高模型的泛化能力和性能，特别是在有限标签数据的情况下，通过预先学习数据的结构，可以在监督任务中获得更好的表现。</a:t></a:r><a:endParaRPr><a:latin typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:ea typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:cs typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:sym typeface="+mn-ea"/></a:endParaRPr></a:p><a:p><a:endParaRPr><a:latin typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:ea typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:cs typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:sym typeface="+mn-ea"/></a:endParaRPr></a:p><a:p><a:r><a:rPr><a:latin typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:ea typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:cs typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:sym typeface="+mn-ea"/></a:rPr><a:t>辅助学习范式指的是辅助任务或学习方法，用于改进主要对比学习任务的性能。这些辅助任务旨在提供额外的监督信号或额外的学习目标，以改善模型在对比学习任务上的表现。</a:t></a:r><a:endParaRPr><a:latin typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:ea typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:cs typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:sym typeface="+mn-ea"/></a:endParaRPr></a:p><a:p><a:r><a:rPr><a:latin typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:ea typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:cs typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:sym typeface="+mn-ea"/></a:rPr><a:t>这些辅助学习范式为对比学习任务提供了额外的信息或目标，有助于改善模型的泛化能力、特征学习效果和性能表现。辅助学习任务的选择和设计在对比学习中扮演着关键角色，因为它们可以使模型更好地理解数据，提取更丰富和有用的特征。</a:t></a:r><a:endParaRPr><a:latin typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:ea typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:cs typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:sym typeface="+mn-ea"/></a:endParaRPr></a:p></p:txBody></p:sp><p:sp><p:nvSpPr><p:cNvPr id="4" name="灯片编号占位符 3"/><p:cNvSpPr><a:spLocks noGrp="1"/></p:cNvSpPr><p:nvPr><p:ph type="sldNum" sz="quarter" idx="5"/></p:nvPr></p:nvSpPr><p:spPr/><p:txBody><a:bodyPr/><a:p><a:fld id="{1D0EAFC4-830A-47E7-8F93-2C2D15D9C629}" type="slidenum"><a:rPr lang="zh-CN" altLang="en-US" smtClean="0"/></a:fld><a:endParaRPr lang="zh-CN" altLang="en-US"/></a:p></p:txBody></p:sp></p:spTree></p:cSld><p:clrMapOvr><a:masterClrMapping/></p:clrMapOvr></p:notes>